Percussion (2019-08-29)

  • This is a control pig. The pig was not instrumented at all. Only artery and venous lines are put in for infusing contrast, propofol, fetanyl, replacement fluids and pressure monitoring. Foley catheter put into bladder. Rectal temperature probe.

Maintain Rectal temp at 38 +/- 0.5 deg.

Study: 13:45 pm - 01:45 am (next day - 12h).

b) 2nd phase: 10 images at 15s intervals

The baseline (0) and 1 h CTP scan failed because the slice location for the phase 1 and phase acquisition did not line up.
